Package com.oap2024team7.team7mediastreamingapp.models

Class Profile

java.lang.Object
com.oap2024team7.team7mediastreamingapp.models.Profile
public class Profile extends Object
Class for the Profile object. This class represents a profile of a customer in the application. It stores the profile ID, customer ID, profile name, birth date and hashed password. It also stores a boolean value to indicate if the profile is the main profile of the customer. The profile ID is automatically assigned by the database when a new profile is created.
Author:
Agata (Agy) Olaussen (@agyCoding)
